Kitchensink notes:

  • When updating the form please follow the ordering and naming pattern.
  • Components have a regular (default named) version with required to test formatting of values, and a version that is not required (to test empty values)
  • Components that support it have a multiple-values version both with- and without required.
  • Most components have a version for hidden with a default and extra variations
